<P>
   COXNET ENTERTAIN _ COXNET-ENTERTAINMENT 0129 -- ``Frasier'' has
picked up a few nicks and scrapes in recent months, as Frasier's
long layoff seemed to turn off a lot of fans. At the same time, the
show moved into the ``Seinfeld'' time slot, and while it increased
its own ratings, it couldn't measure up to the hallowed last season
of Jerry's gang. But the star and the cast of the NBC are looking
to turn things around. (Kloer, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
