   WITH
</P>
<P>
   STAR FILE _ The thing about Ling is, nobody on ``Ally McBeal''
stands a chance against her. This season's most-noticed breakout TV
character, Ling Woo has cold cat eyes, the charm (and kick) of an
antifreeze cocktail, a penchant for bizarre lawsuits and, when it
suits her purposes, the ability to put men in brain lock with her
sexual teasing. (Kloer, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   RINGEL ON VIDEO _ Husband-and-wife teams appearing together is
hardly a rarity in Hollywood. Not all the marriages survived. Not
all the movies worked. But if you want to check out the on-screen
chemistry of some of Hollywood's more famous wedded couples, here
are a few ideas. (Ringel, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
