full of male bonding, bar fights, passion and obsession. Grade: B-.
(StMurray, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   REVIEW-CRAZY _ Review of ``Still Crazy,'' a comedy. Call it
``The Full Monty'' with a rock band. Stephen Rea and Billy Connolly
star. Grade: A-. (Ringel, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   REVIEW-SHES _ Review of ``She's All That,'' a romantic comedy
about a teenager who bets he can turn the school's geekiest girl
into a prom queen _ and then falls in love with her. Stars Freddie
Prinze Jr. and Rachael Leigh Cook. Usher in credits, too. Grade: C
(StMurray, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
