<DOCNO> NYT19990128.0118 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-28 13:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2344 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BOOK-RED-BOS &LR;      01-28 0857
