<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-28 15:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2441 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-STRUGGLING-BOOKSHOP-H     01-28 0995
