A2603 &Cx1f; tad-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-IOC-GANGA-0129-COX     01-28 0597
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-IOC-GANGA-0129-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    CONGO'S GANGA VOWS TO FIGHT EXPULSION FROM IOC
 &HT;    Moving in both the (i) International and (s) Sports categories.
