Harvard students, children under 18 and everyone on Wednesdays and
Saturdays from 10 a.m. to noon. Information: (617) 495-9400.
</P>
<P>
   AMERICAN REPERTORY THEATER, Loeb Drama Center, 64 Brattle St.,
Cambridge, (617) 547-8300. The premiere of Don DeLillo's
``Valparaiso.'' Friday and Saturday nights at 8; Sunday at 2 and 7
p.m. Through March 17. The play will run in repertory with ``The
Master Builder,'' whose previews begin Feb. 12. Through March 21.
Tickets: $23 to $55.
</P>
<P>
   Getting There
</P>
<P>
   BY AIR: Delta Shuttle, (800) 933-5935. Every hour on the half
hour from La Guardia's Marine Terminal to Logan Airport's Terminal
B in Boston. With 14-day advance reservation, $168 round trip, plus
