<P>
   BBC-GATECH-PREVIEW _ Expectations are high for the Georgia Tech
baseball team this season, which is ranked among the top three
teams in the nation. The Jackets begin their quest for the College
World Series today against Auburn in the Disney Baseball Blast in
Orlando. (Arey, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 20.
</P>
<P>
   GOLF
</P>
<P>
   GLF-DUVAL _ David Duval tries to keep the magic going in the
opening round of the Phoenix Open. He won his second tournament in
two tries Sunday, shooting a record 59 in Las Vegas. (Sheeley,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 7.
</P>
<P>
   GLF-GEORGE-COLUMN _ Dave George column from the Office Depot
LPGA tournament. (George, Palm Beach Post).
