<HEADER>
A2889 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPOT-BUDGET-BOS &LR;      01-28 0608
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPOT-BUDGET-BOS </SLUG>
  
 For Release FRIDAY AMs, January 29, 1999  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Boston Globe plans to move the following stories for use by
NYTimes News Service clients.
</P>
<P>
