<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-28 19:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2939 &Cx1f; tad-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ARENA-NAME29-COX     01-28 0391
