   AMGEN-EARNINGS (Los Angeles) _ Biotechnology drug developer
Amgen Inc. handily beat analysts' expectations Thursday with a 33
percent gain in fourth quarter earnings. Amgen, which announced the
results after the close of trading, reported net income of 90 cents
per share compared to 67 cents per share in the fourth quarter a
year ago. By Ben Sullivan. (Will move in the ``f'' financial news
file.)
