A2953 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-SOCSEC-ASSE     01-28 0032
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-SOCSEC-ASSESS-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
