<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SUPER BOWL XXXIII
 &HT;    BUDGET FOR PAPERS OF FRIDAY, JAN. 29
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDs: Here is the Cox News Service Super Bowl budget for papers
