   FBN-BENNETT _ MIAMI _ There's a good reason Falcons linebacker
Cornelius Bennett is proclaiming himself this year's John Elway:
After four unsuccessful Super appearances, he thinks this is his
year. He enters this game with more fans than he had last year _
they are located in cellblock C in Buffalo. That's where Bennett
spent much of the summer. (Winkeljohn, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 25-30.
