<P>
   COMMENTARY (``k'' category)
</P>
<P>
   MEANS-COLUMN (Washington) _ Among the tortured last-minute
maneuvers of Senate Republicans searching for an exit from
President Clinton's impeachment trial were efforts to drag him
personally back on to center stage, as if constantly befouling his
name were not enough. By MARIANNE MEANS. (Already filed.)
